<h2 class="sectionedit1"><a name="top" id="top">top</a></h2>
<div class="level2">

<p>
Sintassi:
</p>
<pre class="cpp code cpp">    <span class="co2">#include &lt;stack&gt;</span>
    T<span class="sy3">&amp;</span> top<span class="br0">&#40;</span><span class="br0">&#41;</span><span class="sy4">;</span></pre>
<p>
La funzione top() ritorna una reference all&#039;elemento in cima allo stack.
</p>

<p>
L&#039;esempio seguente rimuove tutti gli elementi dallo stack e usa top() per 
mostrarli:
</p>
<pre class="cpp code cpp">     <span class="kw1">while</span><span class="br0">&#40;</span> <span class="sy3">!</span>s.<span class="me1">empty</span><span class="br0">&#40;</span><span class="br0">&#41;</span> <span class="br0">&#41;</span> <span class="br0">&#123;</span>
       <span class="kw3">cout</span> <span class="sy1">&lt;&lt;</span> s.<span class="me1">top</span><span class="br0">&#40;</span><span class="br0">&#41;</span> <span class="sy1">&lt;&lt;</span> <span class="st0">&quot; &quot;</span><span class="sy4">;</span>
       s.<span class="me1">pop</span><span class="br0">&#40;</span><span class="br0">&#41;</span><span class="sy4">;</span>
     <span class="br0">&#125;</span></pre>
<p>

Argomenti correlati: <a href="pop" class="wikilink1" title="it:container:stack:pop">pop</a>
</p>

